bug.short_desc: [i18n]texts are not externalized in "team repositories" view

long_desc.thetext:
Created attachment 225803 sample images
Hello, I hope this report could be useful. I find many texts are not externalized in the Team Repositories view and some related view. I surround the texts with red frame.
In attachement; 1) mylyn_1.PNG shows 1 text is not externalized at menu | window | show view | other | Mylyn . 2) mylyn_2.PNG shows many texts are also not, at the Team Repositories view. 2) mylyn_3.PNG shows 2 texts are also not. this page can be shown with New | Repository, after right click on the view.
Thanks.
See https://git.eclipse.org/r/#/c/12995/ for Tasks and https://git.eclipse.org/r/#/c/12996/ for Commons (Team Repos). Feel free to provide additional patches in case I missed anything.
Thank You for co-operation, I can confirm this issue is fixed.
